results.description:
Refresh your home to express and impress without the hard work of redecorating.
32 Bright colours to choose from including 3 metallic colours.
No tacky plastic background or outline.


RELIABILITY
Unlike many other cheaper alternatives, we cut your products from Italian manufactured Ritrama Monomeric gloss finish vinyl. With a 5-year exterior life and upwards of 10 years indoors. A perfectly smooth vinyl Decal with no bubbles or creases after application. 

ADAPTABLE MATERIALS
Products from our store can be used indoors or outdoors and applied to most surfaces.
No colour loss/fade if you choose to apply your Decal on a vehicle or in direct sunlight.
Decals can be re-positioned while applying to your surface.
Recommended surfaces include: Walls, Windows, Mirrors, Plastic, Tile, Vehicle Paint and Windows.
Even if the surface isn't perfectly smooth the application process will be.

ZERO MESS
All Decals have application tape pre-applied in our shop, no messing, no extra products needed. 
Clear instructions are sent out with every order.
Long lasting and easily applied.

POSTAGE AND SHIPPING
Royal Mail 1st class tracked with a tracking number sent to you (1-2 Business days)
Parcel Force 24 hour (products over 90cm on the shortest side will be sent with this service FREE)
Shipped in a hardened postal tube.
If you live in an area where Royal Mail and Parcelforce do not deliver to, we will look for the next best and fastest shipping method.

Completely change the feel of a room, vehicle, school, or business with one of our easy to apply Decals.
Redecorating can be stressful in any aspect and we understand that. If you would like your Decal reversed/mirrored or if our sizes are not what you're looking for, send us a message and we will make a custom Decal to meet your requirements.
Orders exceeding £100 will be shipped Parcelforce 24-hour Service.


Check out some of our other Items, We're sure you will find something you love.

results.title: Christmas gift with PHOTOS- PERSONALiZED Photo Blocks- Set of 13- LIVE Laugh LOVE- custom lettering, photos and colors
results.description:
PLEASE NOTE: Our official cutoff dates are as follows: 
MOTHER'S DAY- April 22nd
FATHER'S DAY- May 27th
GRANDPARENTS' DAY- August 19th
CHRISTMAS- December 1st

Orders placed after the cut off date will be put on our waiting list, and will be completed in the order they are received. We will do our very best to get as many orders out as possible... we work like crazy people during the holidays! If you have questions for us, we will do our best to get back to you asap, but please remember to read through the directions that are included in the item descriptions before sending a message... and PLEASE include the date of your order, if you're already on our list!

Don't forget that we would be happy to ship directly to the gift recipient, and no time is a bad time to give a gift that is sure to bring joy to whoever your loved one is... who doesn't love pictures of their favorite people- young, old or FURRY!?! ;)
***PLEASE READ THROUGH ALL DIRECTIONS HERE***



OUR NORMAL TURN AROUND TIME IS 3-4 WEEKS… if you need your order sooner, please message me! We can almost always accommodate requests, but there may be a rush fee, depending on the timing.

ORDERING INSTRUCTIONS: All of our items are custom made, so there’s no need to request a custom item, if you already know what size you’d like. Our pricing is based on size and the amount of wording (one letter as part of a set, name/phrase/date, etc., or a poem). 

1- PURCHASE- Please add the item(s) to your cart- Etsy will automatically combine the shipping- and complete your payment. If you’d like to use a credit card, please choose PayPal as your payment option- you do not need to have a PayPal account to complete your order. Please make sure the shipping address is correct when you make the payment and if you’d like us to ship directly to the gift recipient, you can add their address before processing the payment as well.

2- INFO FORM- Once the payment is made, you will receive the info form in the message to buyer portion of your Etsy receipt (via email). This is where you can add your color choices, wording, special instructions and any other details. Please be sure to confirm the shipping address, and let us know if the address on the form is different from what is on your PayPal payment. There’s also a space for your requested delivery date. You will be asked to EMAIL this form and your photos to us. Please do not send them through the Etsy conversation.

3- CONFIRMATION- We will confirm receipt of your photos- usually within 24 hours. If you have not received this confirmation within 3 days (we try to take the weekends off- but that rarely happens!), please email us.

4- PROOFS- We will send proofs for approval or changes. Sometimes proofs take up to three weeks, depending on the time of year. If you have not received your proofs 5 days before your requested delivery date, please email us.

5- SHIPPING- We always ship via 2-day Priority Mail- this does not necessarily mean 2 days though, and we do our best to ship asap, but if you’d like your order guaranteed to arrive in one or two days, the only option is to upgrade to Express Mail. We would be happy to send an additional invoice to cover the price difference. You will receive the tracking info from PayPal shipping as soon as I print your label… this will go to the email address associated with your PayPal account, or whatever you entered when you made your payment. If you do not receive the tracking info, just send me an email, and I will forward it to you.

6- PROBLEM- if there is ever a problem with your order, please contact us, and we will fix it right away. It is rare, but mistakes happen! ;)

7- LOVE YOUR ORDER- please share our business with your family and friends, and if you want to post a photo to our Facebook page, please feel free! We love our customers, and love to see photos!  https://www.facebook.com/wastenotrecycledart/

Thanks so much for your business and HAPPY ETSY SHOPPING!

results.title: Live Laugh Love Family Home Quote Wall Stickers Art Room, Laptop, Car Decals Diy
results.description:
This is a die-cut vinyl & are one colour with no background - not reusable.

The stickers comes applied with transfer tape (when this is required)

Our stickers will stick to any smooth and clean surface such as metal, glass, cars, walls, doors, windows, laptops, iPads, cabinets, appliances, etc. - Anywhere you want !

Depending on the sizes, our decals may come in separate pieces for easy installation.

To apply a vinyl decal with multiple pieces design, remove it from the paper backing by peeling away the transfer tape; The tape will hold the individual pieces of your sticker design in place while you position it on your desired surface. Once your sticker is positioned, you can press the transfer tape onto a surface to adhere it then slowly peal off the transfer tape - only the decal should remain on the surface - instructions supplied with every order!

Photos are not to scale.

Please check out our other items in our store. If you have any questions just drop us a message.
